    text: "Mr. Tom Kelly, a well-known pugilist of the city, takes a benefit tomorrow evening at the Theatre Comique. Tom Allen, the champion, will box with Kelly in the crib scene from \"Tom and Jerry.\" Bauer, the champion wrestler, together with well-known gladiators of the Graeco-Roman school, will add to the attractions. The benefit promises to be very attractive and furnish rare sport.",
    summary: "Tom Allen joins pugilist Tem Kelly at the Theatre Comique, blending sport and theater in a unique 19th-century spectacle featuring wrestling champion Bauer and Graeco-Roman gladiators."
