    title: "Tom Allen, Former Champion Pugilist and Ex Detective Jack Williams Among the Accused",
    localCopyEdited: "images/articles/image-187.jpg",
    id: "187",
    text: "He is charged by warrant with murder in the second degree.\n\nWithout waiting for the transcript of the record in the case, the Prosecuting Attorney issued a warrant Tuesday afternoon for the arrest of Tom Allen, whom he charges with murder in the second degree, in the killing of Timothy Conroy, Sunday morning.\n\nAllen was at once arrested and gave bond in the sum of $5000. He had previously been acquitted by the Coroner's Jury.",
    summary: "In an era intertwining sports and legal issues, former champion pugilist Tom Allen was arrested for second-degree murder, despite Coroner's Jury acquittal, revealing 19th-century societal tensions."
