    localCopyEdited: "images/articles/image-260.jpg",
    id: "260",
    text: "TOM ALLEN GAVE BOND.\nReleased From Custody on Bail in the\nSum of $5000.\n\nTom Allen, charged with the murder of\nTimothy Confoy, was admitt>ad to $5000\nbond ip Judge Klein's cout Thursday\nmorning. Thomas J. Rowe, 619 Ma\nstreot, went his bond —.",
    summary: "In a pivotal 19th-century boxing legal case, Tom Allen, charged with murdering Timothy Confoy, was released on $5000 bail, highlighting the era's often violent sports culture."
